description: “Starstalker” part 1 of 2! How has the aftermath of the War of Kings affected the newly reborn and viciously battered Nova Corps? When the universe is changed, who is left to protect and serve the innocents? Out of the devastation—and from Marvel’s cosmic past—strides a mysterious new threat...and an unexpected ally!
name: Starstalker, Part 1

description: Despite already being badly hurt, teen ninja Ricky Feeple, now grown into a man, goes a daring freedom fighter mission to rescue the heroes and super-beings that the insane warlord Yuudai has captured over the past ten years. His former teammate, Kuro Katana, now knows Yuudai killed his brother, and he'll stop at nothing to claim his revenge. But when the spell surrounding Quagmire is broken and its fused world starts unraveling, none of them may survive the result!

name: Jughead's Journal; A Lass from the Past

description: Meet Claudia, frigid rich bitch. A little implant in the right spot, a remote, turn the knob: she's a hot cauldron of insatiable lust at your control!

Since the day he first flew over Metropolis, the Man of Steel has been a hero of mythological proportions. Whether saving the world or defending America, the Last Son of Krypton has proven that the true measure of a man is his actions and not his abilities. SUPERMAN: THE ACTION COMICS ARCHIVES VOL. 3 presents the original adventures that are now the foundation of Superman's legendary status. Influenced by the Max Fleischer animated Superman cartoons of the 1940s, this stunning book showcases the Man of Steel as he takes on the villainy of Domino, the genius of the Trickster, the dementia of the Puzzler, and the deadliness of the super-powered Lex Luthor and his incredible Powerstone.
name: Volume 3

description: Don't miss this thrilling archive featuring some of Superman's earliest adventures by his creators, Siegel and Shuster! This volume includes ACTION COMICS #69-85, from 1944-1945.
name: Volume 5

description: In this book, Claudia makes a documentary for CNN, where she tries to unearth not so innocent events performed by a cult which tries to contact aliens. Also, a subplot about woman called Anna Rita, who evades (or tries to evade) an evil, greedy man. And of course, alot of sex...

For some reason, Claudia is back together with his ex-husband. He is working as the lawyer of a company that has made dozens of people blind. One of those is the father of a young woman. She wants to avenge what has happened to her father. She figures that the best way to do so is to create a sex-scandal by using Claudia, and therefore bring her husband to shame. But how? Maybe with an even more powerful "magic box"...

Poor Gepetto. Alone and horny for a beautiful woman. What if he carved the woman of his dreams into a big puppet? Better than nothing... but then, wait, taking her acts like magic in making her real! Lushly rendered by the Frenchman Gibrat, this sexy spoof of the classic tale has poor innocent Pinocchia taken by many a cynic. And when she lies, guess what becomes bigger...

Her son Franklin has never known her terrible secret... he never knew where she spent her evenings... but someone has to pick up the torch... someone has to continue the legacy. Franklin's life is about to change drastically.
name: Punisher 2099

Rodimus Prime and the Autobots of the future arrive in the present day and come face-to-face with Optimus Prime. But something is wrong. The natural laws of universe restores balance to this unnatural situation and Optimus Prime and several of his Autobot colleges disappear.

Optimus Prime, still in limbo speaking through the Matrix, explains to them that the rift in time and space is caused by Cyclonus and Scourge bypassing the mass transference and upsetting the natural balance of the universe.

description: Time is running out as the rift in space grows ever larger reaching out to the Earths surface. The Autobot and Decepticon alliance finally engage Galvatron and Megatron in battle and a severely injured Scourge persuades Ravage to get Cyclonos' body in an attempt to close the rift.

description: Optimus Prime returns from limbo and battles the damaged Galvatron. But this isn't the past the Galvatron remembers through Megatrons eyes. History has changed. As the fight reaches its climax the rift in timespace touches down on top of Galvatron, ripping him apart as he is sucked into the vortex. All seems lost as the rift begins to rip the Earth apart untill Scourge sacrifices himself and then Shockwave arrives throwing the remains of Cyclonus into the rift. With Galvatron, Scourge and Cyclonus consumed by the rift the natural balance to the universe is restored. The concluding part of Time Wars.
name: Time Wars, Part 7
